data.description: This 2 bedroom 1 Bathroom rancher style home, boasts some serious amenities! Tank-less hot water heater, central AC, gas forced air, vinyl windows,  vinyl Siding, and plenty of parking on this oversized corner lot ! Fresh paint throughout most of the home and new vinyl flooring in the kitchen and laundry area and bathroom with beautiful hardwood throughout the rest of the home is sure to set up its new owner for success! All appliances stay including the homes security system and shed.
